HEADWORD: Fore-topgallant
<hw>Fore`-top*gal"lant</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>Designating the mast, sail, yard, etc., above
the topmast; <as>as, the <ex>fore-topgallant</ex> sail</as>. See
<er>Sail</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
